      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i keep walking into the kitchen thinking i'll hear his collar jingle or see him waiting by the bowl, but then i remember. the house feels so heavy. honestly i'm just so tired of carrying this around. i don't think i have any strength left to keep going like this.",
